{"type": "article", "id": 59083, "title": "唯品会“三折封顶”广告遭吐槽，Virgil Abloh 成为依云的创意顾问 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-12-07T04:37:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 419, "name": "创意"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}, {"id": 4386, "name": "唯品会"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181207121911FnBEalJKjk19bYCL.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一看的case</h3><p line=\"rDRS\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4314176996344186?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>旅行青蛙和蚂蚁花呗的戏精花小呗组成“花蛙 CP”环游世界，</b></a>打卡旅行青蛙的梦想地清单。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201812071219577HQZOBjfemsyYkDI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703590\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><p line=\"j5PI\">此外，花呗还推出了“走蛙，和花小呗看世界”主题短片，通过拍摄旅行明信片的旅行青蛙的经典形式和花小呗的惯有吐槽，来展现这次跨界合作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=f08083jmb0g\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t\r\n</div><p line=\"sTn0\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4314343057313280?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>唯品会的 “123” 广告遭到猛烈吐槽。</b></a>那条长达 10 分钟的广告片已经删除，几乎所有 KOL 的推送也都不见了。然而 6 日晚间唯品会又发了条新微博，公布了这次活动的海报。</p><p line=\"sTn0\">本次“三折封顶”的广告的代理商是之外创意（Z+），它之前帮华帝策划出了火热一时的“法国队夺冠，华帝退全款”活动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018120712210154PnU6zmbXkOWF9Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.340741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"hFbu\"><b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">临近“</a><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">双</a><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 12”</a><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">，淘宝发布了</a><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">“</a><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2018</a><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">中国直男图鉴</a><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4313880094735822?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">”。</a></b>通过平台数据分析之后，上海男人最想变高。此外，淘宝还发布了“他经济”的男性消费报告，男性消费特点是追潮流、养生、会玩……还有“养生”？</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181207122127hu3PXsxFnEyracoJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.924855\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181207122127x4aE7VbFLRGlh1AZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.931884\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"ClUM\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4314314040712692?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"\"><b>喜茶全国第 4 家 PINK 主题店今天在上海新天地广场开业，</b></a>这也是喜茶在上海的首家该主题门店。之前喜茶在先后在深圳、广州和南京开了 PINK 主题店，这一主题店的开业瞄准了女性消费者。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812071221575G8oWcfX7aRO1Vrg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812071221575sHvISQUNLETuCzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181207122157lshWvbCYaLtBTc3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181207122157uDBm5qw9Sf63eExK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"rhgr\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4312846663651301?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>苏泊尔在成都开了家“好好饭肆”快闪店，</b></a>又是通过线下体验，来宣传苏泊尔本釜电饭煲可以烹饪出美味的柴火饭。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181207122214YSC2HxTRfteQrWDu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181207122214PbcCvVBsNeh2WuOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812071222145rohaR3vwzPBIksj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812071222156bjzdFveME1G3YI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"s6m2\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4312498004231918?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Charlotte Tilbury 和野兽派打造了中国大陆地区的首个跨境快闪店，</b></a>位于深圳万象天地的野兽派概念便利店 Little B。现场有专业彩妆团队专门讲解护肤和妆容。Charlotte Tilbury 的产品不仅可以在现场选购，也可以到野兽派官网以及 APP 进行购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181207122313wLvOYCFEeS1HB84N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.849558\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812071222359uxMko1r6XwYeEy8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812071222358YJTE1dfWwBAj45c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181207122235H6TqrPeKIpLSaU5o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"4fV8\">Surface Go 发布 2018 年广告片&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8g8ZR0KY7M4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“Grandma Got Run Over by a Reindeer Remix”</b></a>，这是微软有史以来最小的电脑。然而在广告中 10 岁的小女孩一直在吐槽竞争对手苹果的 iPad 算不上是真正的电脑，并没有展现 Surface Go 的优势。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d0808l02uzf\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"zlEs\" class=\"\">梅赛德斯奔驰为全新 GLE 拍了支广告片<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=syaTwfhYCWs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>“In the Long Run”</b></a>，中年人脆弱的时候，可以在车里待一待。创意代理商是 antoni GmbH。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=i0808u0o124\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"cr3V\"><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/virgil-abloh-joins-evian-as-creative-adviser-1202924968/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Virgil Abloh 加入依云担任“可持续创新设计创意顾问”。</b></a>Abloh 将帮助设计 Evian 未来的产品，同时利用他的影响力，提高人们对创新在设计和可持续性重要性的认识。</p><p line=\"gay0\"><a href=\"http://m.ebrun.com/310781.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>抖音将在商家店铺详情页内上线“扫码拍视频领券”工具，</b></a>为线下门店导流。知情人士透露，这一功能将于 12 月 30 日上线。</p><p line=\"iBV8\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjg4Mzg5ODA0MA==&amp;mid=2656250294&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=76f314718ab5047cd4a8c0442edbfe62&amp;chksm=987cb461af0b3d77bec63f6cbf14aa3136115b5384f373699a3ce84970b3e16b3368d33a32b6&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1207D66a0upt1PWU1SIoYOTS&amp;key=84e1ab98e194bf2d9f2218ff0c43a8723e4fb3aa87e3a8040abfd1488f3b5761152d5fbddad6a117aba2073dda87359892dbdde971584891e97af6d6f1454f0fd6442953b253cf2882843f1c2b5675d3&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=uPNNo5PU8pKVHzzGjmLIbGFBwuZMWAPgHe2xpzySbfwcILPj6E%2FAFHpN4XH0xTXj\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>星巴克宣布全面升级星享俱乐部，</b></a>这也是星享俱乐部自 2011 年上线以来第一次大改版。此次升级包含只需手机号即可免费入会，每消费 40 元积累一颗星等。</p><p line=\"iBV8\" class=\"\">题图来自：Pixabay</p>"}